{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I think they were probably told not to-- not to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, by then, it was getting very difficult, anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to leave the flat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was allowed to leave the flat, so he-- whatever food we could get, which wasn't much, because you had-- you had-- you-- you were a ration-- ration cards.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you could-- you couldn't-- being Jewish, you couldn't get milk, you couldn't get butter, you couldn't get meat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You  could hardly get anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we did, in fact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a neighbor, and to this day, I think I know who it may have been, but I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every night, there was a tray outside our door with food, the dinner for-- for the lot of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which was a very brave thing to do, because they could've-- they could've paid for it very-- whoever it was, God bless them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we-- so anyway, we were-- so we were-- we were given food by-- by others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Otherwise, we would have been unbelievably hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
